#####################
# CONFIGURAÇÃO LOCAL / SEGREDOS
#####################

# ASP.NET — overrides locais e user secrets
**/appsettings.*.local.json
**/secrets.json

# Dotenv — nunca versionar `.env` real; manter templates `.example`
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
!**/.env.example
!**/.env.*.example

# Terraform — estado e variáveis com dados sensíveis (IPs, chaves SSH, etc.)
**/.terraform/
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.*
**/.terraform.lock.hcl
**/*.tfvars
!**/*.tfvars.example
**/crash.log
**/override.tf
**/override.tf.json
**/*_override.tf
**/*_override.tf.json

# Ansible — inventário gerado (IPs e utilizadores reais)
**/ansible/inventory/hosts.azure.yml
**/ansible/inventory/hosts.aws.yml
**/ansible/inventory/hosts.yml
!**/ansible/inventory/*.example

# Chaves SSH / certificados locais
*.pem
id_rsa
id_ed25519
!*.pub

#####################
# FRONTEND (Node)
#####################
**/node_modules/
